e\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fsa1665703536941.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fsa1665703536941.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fsa1665703536941.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"notoc dita\" id=\"fsa1665703536941\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Optionally create a local <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file for your application that can\n      be specified using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ini</span> command line switch.</p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"fsa1665703536941__context_w3546ab1b5b1_w3547ab1b5_w3548ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fsa1665703536941__p_d177338e1_d177339e1_d177340e1\">When Uniface looks for a setting, it does so in the following order:</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\" id=\"fsa1665703536941__li_d54242e1_d54243e1_d54244e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Local <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file, as specified by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ini</span> switch on the command line\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\" id=\"fsa1665703536941__li_d54245e1_d54246e1_d54247e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> located in location specified by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/adm</span> switch on the command line.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n<section class=\"section result body required-cleanup-multiple-ol-elements-in-topic-body\" id=\"fsa1665703536941__result_w3549ab1b5b5_w3550ab1b5_w3551ab1\">\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"fsa1665703536941__p_d177341e1_d177342e1_d177343e1\">The maximum length of a line in the\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file, whether local or <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>, is\n            4000 characters.<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"fsa1665703536941__note_qwl_vsg_fxb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The limit of the length of a key in a line\n               is 1000 characters, while the limit of the length of a value, that is the value after\n               '=' sign in a line is 3000 characters.</div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fsa1665703536941__p_d177344e1_d177345e1_d177346e1\">The settings are grouped into sections that address specific aspects of the run-time environment.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613106\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613106\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Creating the .ini file Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Optionally create a local .ini file for your application that can be specified using the /ini command line switch. When Uniface looks for a setting, it does so in the following order: Local .ini file, as specified by the /ini switch on the command line usys.ini located in location specified by /adm switch on the command line. The maximum length of a line in the .ini file, whether local or usys.ini , is 4000 characters. Note: The limit of the length of a key in a line is 1000 characters, while the limit of the length of a value, that is the value after '=' sign in a line is 3000 characters. The settings are grouped into sections that address specific aspects of the run-time environment. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}